text: George Smith (22 July 1855 - 7 April 1897) was an Australian cricketer. He played two first-class cricket matches for Victoria between 1877 and 1885. ==See also== * List of Victoria first-class cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1855 births Category:1897 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers Category:Cricketers from Melbourne
